729774f-b.title: Richmond: Trantor Place - Dixon Avenue
729774f-b.text:
Trantor Place, west side, north of Dixon Avenue,
showing the J.W. Barnes house. The view is northeastward
from Dixon Avenue.
March 24, 1928
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
(2)
Ahnother view of the house, seen from Nicholas
Avenue. Trantor Place is the new street being cut through
directly in front of the house.
May 21, 1932
P. L. Sperr
NO REFRODUCTIONS
